  SCOPE OF THE SYSTEM
The Mobile Banking Database System focuses on managing digital banking data 
related to clients, accounts, wallets, transactions, loans, and 
authentication processes.
The system will allow the bank to store, manage, and retrieve financial 
information efficiently.

The system will include:
•	Managing client information
•	Managing bank accounts and wallet balances
•	Recording financial transactions
•	Managing loan records
•	Authenticating users during login
•	Storing device information used to access the system

The system will not include:
•	Physical ATM operations
•	External financial systems integration
•	Mobile application interface development
The focus of the project is the database structure and management of banking data.
